    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Dictyopteris Membranacea Extract (Retired) is the extract of the alga, Dictyopteris membranacea.\r\n\r\nThe INCI Name, Dictyopteris Membranacea Extract, originally published in 2007, was designated with a retired status in 2015. For an interim period of time, trade name assignments formerly published with the INCI Name Dictyopteris Membranacea Extract will be retained in the retired monograph, and also published with the new name assignment based on the current genus and species name, Dictyopteris Polypodioides Extract."
